_sText:
A cool disco map that I made when I was bored,and some ppl wanted 1 so I made it.

Main parts:
-Disco has 8 songs
-Disco ball
-Disco food section 
-Gun Toss
-Can Hold 64 Players

Changes since v4 - Fixes Spawn Points

If you guys think the map is missing something just pm me or comment.

Hope you guys like it...Enjoy
